title: Family fears for life of rapper they say was violently arrested after encouraging Iranians to protest

title: Britons given extra day's holiday to celebrate King's coronation
description: British Prime Minister Rishi Sunak announced Sunday there would be a public holiday to celebrate the coronation of King Charles III next year.
